"contrast, :doc:`installing </user/how-to-guides/how-to-install-software>`"
"       packages using direct package manager commands is fine.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-update.rst:88
#: 541d308347d14d7591046712b96ef849
msgid ""
"Advanced users may wish to perform updates via the command-line "
"interface. There are two ways to do this:"
msgstr ""

