#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-update.rst:96
#: c7e78e37f7884ce688484efac7054482
msgid ""
"Alternatively, use ``qubes-dom0-update`` to update dom0, and use ``qubes-"
"vm-update`` to update domUs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-update.rst:100
#: e89c4c48fc7f4b23af4e9d937f6f967c
msgid ""
"Using either of these methods has the same effect as updating via the "
"Qubes Update tool."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-update.rst:102
#: 59eac0b95bdb4799a4aac866c99fe012
msgid ""
"Advanced users may also be interested in learning :doc:`how to enable the"
