msgstr ""

#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-update.rst:184
#: cdac22e4ae004184b0e75b7eadec0ba4
msgid ""
"If so, `adjust your BIOS settings "
"<https://github.com/fwupd/fwupd/wiki/PluginFlag:capsules-unsupported>`__ "
"to enable UEFI updates. This setting is sometimes named “Windows UEFI "
"Firmware Update.”"
