#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-update.rst:186
#: 4a3ac274bb10460bac24773bc81a8d70
msgid "Once resolved, in a dom0 terminal:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-update.rst:196
#: 7cab90b465be45e9b48ce17c4a0dbd3d
msgid ""
"A numbered list of devices with available updates will be presented. "
"Ensure your computer is plugged in to a stable power source, then type "
"the list number of the device you wish to update. If a reboot is "
